dc_title_s: Kossuth County, Iowa, 1973, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol 19109. Form of individual image numbering: 19109-173-[number] 19109-273-[number] or 19109-373-[number]. Year flown: 1973. Flown by Air Tech Inc. New Richmond Wisc. Scale 1:20000|Contact the Map Collection at The University of Iowa Libraries: http://www.lib.uiowa.edu/maps/contact/|Scanned at 300 ppi in Greyscale.
